{"tid":2069360,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"立法會通過委任 張舉能擔任終院首席法官","createTime":"2020-06-18T10:18:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T19:45:21.000Z","uid":89160,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"428179bb803f51a0323897926f98796350aa3caa","tid":2069360,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T10:18:29.000Z","msg":"民主派投票紀錄<br />\n<br />\n贊成：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">葉建源、李國麟、莫乃光、梁繼昌、郭榮鏗</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n棄權：<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>許智峯、鄺俊宇、黃碧雲、林卓廷、胡志偉、譚文豪、郭家麒、陳淑莊、楊岳橋、張超雄、邵家臻</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n缺席：<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>尹兆堅、涂謹申</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n反對：<strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">梁耀忠、毛孟靜、朱凱廸、陳志全、鄭松泰</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>民主黨就任命張舉能投棄權票 冀帶出法治危在旦夕警號</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532795-20200618.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532795-20200618.htm&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHtDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=7b13341e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532795-20200618.htm&h=220e5245\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532795-20200618.htm</a><br />\n//民主黨投棄權票，議員許智峯說，過往市民相信法治及司法獨立，但現時法治令人憂慮，投棄權票是希望帶出法治危在旦夕的警號，司法獨立岌岌可危，提醒司法機構要制衡政府，而非配合政府。<br />\n本身是大律師的公民黨黨魁楊岳橋說，今次處理有關任命是任重道遠，因為香港已進入「大時代」，張舉能面對的挑戰，包括在新時代下香港人對法治的信心，希望他有勇氣及能力，向全世界展現香港司法獨立不受任何勢力的影響。//"},{"pid":"5a25bd9359eb98db2f34524d9d9ccdde7929f1b8","tid":2069360,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T10:20:01.000Z","msg":"不舉撚"},{"pid":"a8c2c240a8e9281d8730b7cbda262ba969cfeb15","tid":2069360,"uid":89160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T10:22:13.000Z","msg":"立會辯終院首席法官任命 張建宗讚張舉能公正<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1799056/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E8%BE%AF%E7%B5%82%E9%99%A2%E9%A6%96%E5%B8%AD%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98%E4%BB%BB%E5%91%BD-%E5%BC%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%97%E8%AE%9A%E5%BC%B5%E8%88%89%E8%83%BD%E5%85%AC%E6%AD%A3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1799056%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E7%25B5%2582%25E9%2599%25A2%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25AE%2598%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E5%2591%25BD-%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%25AE%2597%25E8%25AE%259A%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E8%2588%2589%25E8%2583%25BD%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%25AD%25A3&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHtDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=3c32067e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1799056%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E7%25B5%2582%25E9%2599%25A2%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25AE%2598%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E5%2591%25BD-%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%25AE%2597%25E8%25AE%259A%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E8%2588%2589%25E8%2583%25BD%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%25AD%25A3&h=a5d846fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1799056/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E8%BE%AF%E7%B5%82%E9%99%A2%E9%A6%96%E5%B8%AD%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98%E4%BB%BB%E5%91%BD-%E5%BC%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%97%E8%AE%9A%E5%BC%B5%E8%88%89%E8%83%BD%E5%85%AC%E6%AD%A3</a><br />\n<br />\n//張建宗形容張舉能是傑出的大律師，加入司法機構逾19年，主管高等法院的司法及行政事務，一直公正不阿，曾處理不少重大及複雜案件，深受法律界敬重，相信能勝任司法機構之首的職責。//<br />\n<br />\n//法律界郭榮鏗表示，業界憂慮「港區國安法」立法後，本港司法獨立受損，期望張舉能接任後堅守原則。民主黨許智峯認為市民對法治失去信心，期望張舉能要確保司法機構擔任制衡政府角色，而非配合當局。//<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">（郭榮鏗投贊成票）</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"c8ca88245afe9368df0ad3003f034a8e3c6d165a","tid":2069360,"uid":89160,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T10:27:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>//民主黨投棄權票是希望帶出法治危在旦夕的警號//</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Well Well Well</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b5eeb4f1819eb7576b104137da63ce34a452701","tid":2069360,"uid":22310,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c8ca88245afe9368df0ad3003f034a8e3c6d165a","tid":2069360,"uid":89160,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T10:27:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>//民主黨投棄權票是希望帶出法治危在旦夕的警號//</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Well Well Well</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T10:31:22.000Z","msg":"哇個警號響到呢"},{"pid":"ad15d30e275026940cffc687be1a20d92c7c0392","tid":2069360,"uid":89160,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"7b5eeb4f1819eb7576b104137da63ce34a452701","tid":2069360,"uid":22310,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c8ca88245afe9368df0ad3003f034a8e3c6d165a","tid":2069360,"uid":89160,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T10:27:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>//民主黨投棄權票是希望帶出法治危在旦夕的警號//</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Well Well Well</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T10:31:22.000Z","msg":"哇個警號響到呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T10:33:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>相信35+都應該會繼續為政府響起「警號」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"0abed90fa5182813f2a1220add00fedeeb0a4f4a","tid":2069360,"uid":184581,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T10:34:53.000Z","msg":"作為上訴庭庭長，他處理過多宗涉及憲法爭議的案件，包括外傭居港權案、游蕙禎及梁頌恆的宣誓DQ案件等。<br />\n<br />\n2017年8月25日，終審法院在預審直接拒絕受理他們的上訴申請，案件宣布終審，兩人議員資格確定無效<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n輸曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ccdded5bdf70d8343f736ba55e512d77041df7","tid":2069360,"uid":89160,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T10:35:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">其實棄權票係咪等如白票/廢票撚？</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"0af5fa2f6488723214a19b36a235ac7bc6fa3176","tid":2069360,"uid":22310,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ad15d30e275026940cffc687be1a20d92c7c0392","tid":2069360,"uid":89160,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"7b5eeb4f1819eb7576b104137da63ce34a452701","tid":2069360,"uid":22310,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c8ca88245afe9368df0ad3003f034a8e3c6d165a","tid":2069360,"uid":89160,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T10:27:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>//民主黨投棄權票是希望帶出法治危在旦夕的警號//</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Well Well Well</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T10:31:22.000Z","msg":"哇個警號響到呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T10:33:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>相信35+都應該會繼續為政府響起「警號」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T10:35:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持35+ 聯合喺立法會議事堂入面響警號"},{"pid":"6c260425e60eceaf40cda97cb672299380600505","tid":2069360,"uid":249885,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T10:37:25.000Z","msg":"郭榮鏗贊成？"},{"pid":"0f23dcfb84e36b99312afb33eec0