憂慮。<br />\n<br />\n獲公民黨豁免可按業界意願投票支持的郭榮鏗發言指，希望香港法官面對政治壓力時無畏無懼，認為中央若公開評論香港案件的裁決，又或對香港法官指指點點，等同向香港法官施加政治干預和壓力：「呢樣應該要避免，因為係不合憲亦不恰當。」他指香港法治面對巨大威脅，法官不能視而不見，一定要謹守各項司法原則，判案要確保程序公義、《基本法》和《國際人權法》列明對港人權利的保障。"},{"pid":"c937465fafc298653f6c5a8d61de9e20a23b8129","tid":2069360,"uid":26770,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T10:44:35.000Z","msg":"葉建源、李國麟、莫乃光、梁繼昌、郭榮鏗<br />\n<br />\n功能組別五賤<br />\n都話左35+一定死係功能組別"},{"pid":"248f3773a5f253aaef860476b4f112dba270ab70","tid":2069360,"uid":28264,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T10:46:53.000Z","msg":"點解民主派又棄權<br />\n怕9月港共拎呢個做理由QD佢地<br />\n如果係 咁姐係政棍啦 怕沒得再選 沒得永續<br />\n就連應該投反對既都唔投<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申:我係熱狗我係鬼我係5毛我係POPO狗"},{"pid":"e7335c474954a2e028ff842dfd2cf5afcc10ea9e","tid":2069360,"uid":94968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T10:48:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9f536e8c9d8c742e395466ad0cf82964acd3542","tid":2069360,"uid":89160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T10:51:23.000Z","msg":"北區區議員蔣旻正擬出選教育界  挑戰葉建源  斥教協拒初選 <br />\n教協：時間緊逼難參與<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">葉建源投贊成票</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%8C%97%E5%8D%80%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E8%94%A3%E6%97%BB%E6%AD%A3%E6%93%AC%E5%87%BA%E9%81%B8%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E7%95%8C-%E6%8C%91%E6%88%B0%E8%91%89%E5%BB%BA%E6%BA%90-%E6%96%A5%E6%95%99%E5%8D%94%E6%8B%92%E5%88%9D%E9%81%B8-%E6%95%99%E5%8D%94-%E6%99%82%E9%96%93%E7%B7%8A%E9%80%BC%E9%9B%A3%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258C%2597%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593